# Project Commands

When the user says **"Run the project"** (or similar: start the project, run the app):
- Execute `npm start` from the project root (runs `./start.sh` - backend + frontend)

When the user says **"Stop the project"** (or similar: stop the app):
- Execute `npm run stop` from the project root (runs `./stop.sh` - kills ports 8000 and 5173)
